{"tid":1712081,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中大有學生懷疑頭部中彈倒地　懷疑失去意識","createTime":"2019-11-12T13:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T23:42:21.000Z","uid":20933,"like":135,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"39e22d358eb6354ebca170773abd2637ef6ecb94","tid":1712081,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1491681_1_20191112211458.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1491681_1_20191112211458.jpg&h=deb4d989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大晚上爆發新一輪衝突。防暴警察持續在二號橋向中大校園方向的學生防線，不斷發射催淚彈及橡膠子彈，情況陷入一片混亂，多名學生及示威者受傷，有學生懷疑頭部中彈倒地，懷疑失去意識，義務急救員治理，在場人士不斷叫他叫蘇醒，要召喚救護車急救。<br />\n<br />\n多名學生受傷，有人頭破血流，大批義務急救員為傷者檢查，有傷者眼晴未能睜開，在場人士用清水和茶，為吸入催淚彈的學生洗眼。<br />\n<br />\n新一輪的衝突在晚上7時半後發生，中大校長段崇智當時正前往二號橋，計劃與警方作進一步的商討，但在場警員指，現時不是談判的時候，段崇智無法控制背後的人，要求他離開，並即時發放多枚催淚彈，距離段崇智不足50米，段崇智距離在其他職員護送下離開，有示威者架設防線，阻止警方推進，有人向警方投擲汽油彈還擊，雙方仍在對峙，現場一遍火海。"},{"pid":"cc56fb21a22f75518ab636883169e4c8970bd241","tid":1712081,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:21:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491681-20191112.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491681-20191112.htm&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7Q8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=a187886d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491681-20191112.htm&h=82f0ec1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491681-20191112.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0ecf939d163006bab8699f57e11ed04a9ae8ff9a","tid":1712081,"uid":279253,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:21:29.000Z","msg":"手足啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂住啊"},{"pid":"03bb1469b3ebabfed5e0e2d9fdf69e52b0693df0","tid":1712081,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56d6315fdefd5cc698b90e206904ff73575467a","tid":1712081,"uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/CmyrFgR.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"904ceb4a09a9fe9d488675d9fa66b8aad60b244c","tid":1712081,"uid":90601,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:23:09.000Z","msg":"遠水不能救近火！！只係各地開花，班狗可以用無警時份唔理你！！<br />\n<br />\n分頭行事！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主力反包！<br />\n另小隊開花！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中大地理難去，但去到就去！人多就咩都有可能！求下大家！！"},{"pid":"c65feff16558d2cc282b800771b544e758a85957","tid":1712081,"uid":248588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57932f10d0f749b57040b74376ed4679fb099ea7","tid":1712081,"uid":237077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:23:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中大物資：<br />\n唔要水/食物<br />\n要冰袖、冰袋、機油、電油、白電油、汽油、大量長遮、豬嘴、濾罐、風機、頭盔大量、索帶、雨褸</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9a8163eb6edb5cfa9497ac6d9859d678eee02407","tid":1712081,"uid":89727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:23:41.000Z","msg":"頂住啊手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd2f22cff4470489fb78f06cde34d774510a7f8","tid":1712081,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-